com.thinkaurelius.titan.graphdb.query

Interface TitanPredicate

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.tinkerpop.blueprints.Predicate
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Cmp, Contain, Geo, Text

    public interface TitanPredicate
extends com.tinkerpop.blueprints.Predicate
    Titan's extension of Blueprint's Predicate interface. Contains some custom methods that Titan needs for query answering and evaluation.

    This class contains a subclass used to convert Blueprint's Predicate to the corresponding Titan predicates.
    Author:
    Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
